items.name: BlazingTool
items.description: Brute force ethereum wallet mnemonics. Multi-threaded and suprisingly fast. automatically generate seed phrases and check balances for Ethereum networks. If a wallet with a non-zero balance is found, the wallet's information (address, mnemonic, private key, and balances) is logged and saved to a file named result.txt.

items.name: CrystalTool
items.description: Crypto Wallet Cracker is a powerful tool for cracking cryptocurrency wallet passwords by brute force. It is designed to systematically brute force all possible password combinations until the correct one is found, allowing unauthorized access to the wallet.
